data.description: This remodeled property offers a spacious and modern living space, perfect for families or individuals seeking comfort and convenience. The home features five well-appointed bedrooms, providing ample space for relaxation and privacy. With three beautifully designed bathrooms, residents can enjoy the luxury of convenience and functionality. The property's recent remodeling ensures a contemporary aesthetic, showcasing updated fixtures and finishes throughout. This home presents an excellent opportunity for potential buyers seeking a stylish and comfortable living environment. This homes offers two private guest quarters with its own separate entrance.
